These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, badminton, sailing, skateboarding, water-polo
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, april, october, march, january
The people have 5 different jobs:  pilot, project-manager, designer, software-developer, dancer
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, skateboard, van, bus
 1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the pilot is on the left of the designer##1
 8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the project-manager and the person who's birthday is in january##2
12. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the dancer is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Sport      | swimming        | badminton | water-polo     | sailing   | skateboarding |
| Birthday   | october     | april      | march | january   | december    |
| Job   | software-developer  | project-manager     | pilot | designer | dancer  |
| Transport           | bike | skateboard      | bus     | van   | motorbike     |

