.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, 7up, hot-chocolate, juice
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero, romance, zombie, horror
City: edinburgh, prague, nizza, paris, colone
There 5 different types of food: pomegranate, broccoli, raspberry, cherry, spinach
 1. the person eating spinach is in the middle##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 5. the person eating broccoli is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person watching horror movies##2
 6. the person eating cherry is the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | milk | juice    | lemonade  | 7up    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | superhero       | romance      | martial-arts | zombie        |
| City   | colone   | prague     | edinburgh    | paris  | nizza     |
| Food     | raspberry    | broccoli | spinach | cherry | pomegranate |

