.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, august, january, october, april
There are 5 different nationalities: american, thai, japanese, turkish, egyptian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, davidoff, swisher, pall-mall, havana
The people use 5 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi, train, skateboard, airplane
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is the davidoff-smoker##1
 2. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the american is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 7. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 8. the american is on the right of the thai##1
 9. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is the turkish##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
13. the person driving the airplane is between the egyptian and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Birthday         | february | april     | january   | august   | october |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | thai | american | turkish | japanese        |
| Cigar   | swisher      | davidoff      | pall-mall       | havana       | cain       |
| Transport         | taxi | airplane  | skateboard    | quad-bike    | train        |

