 4. the cain-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in june and the librarian##2
 5. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the coach##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is the bolivar-smoker##1
11. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
12. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
13. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
