.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, adventure, animation, superhero, fantasy
There are 5 different favourite colors: mauve, aquamarine, ebony, yellow, lavender
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, soul, trance, gospel, techno
5 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, monopoly, poker, bridge
 1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the fan dubstep##1
 2. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is between the person playing billiard and the person who likes mauve##2
 5. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the fan soul##1
 8. the fan techno is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fan dubstep##1
11. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
12. the fan gospel is on the left of the fan dubstep##1
13. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero       | fantasy       | romance   | animation      | adventure    |
| Color       | lavender | yellow        | mauve       | ebony       | aquamarine |
| Music-Genre        | techno     | soul        | gospel | dubstep        | trance  |
| Game      | poker | monopoly | backgammon      | bridge | billiard  |

