 8. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who likes black##2
12. the person eating kale is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
13. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
