 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is in the middle##1
11. the pilot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5     |
| Job      | security-guard | lawyer | software-developer   | pilot | videographer     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | western  | superhero    | time-travel          | drama |
| Cigar         | aristoff | dunhill  | pall-mall | tiparillo    | game      |
| Birthday     | february  | april   | november    | july          | october      |

