.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, canasta, scrabble, go
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, horse, snake, cat, hamster
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, musical, disaster, crime, family
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, pall-mall, alhambra, game, fonseca
 1. the person watching family movies is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person watching musical movies##2
 2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person playing bridge is the owner of the cat##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
11. the alhambra-smoker is between the person watching disaster movies and the owner of the snake##2
12. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
